high_descs: Turn around and exit this room, then go left through the hall straight to the kitchen, turning left to the fridge.
Remove the pan from the fridge.
Turn around to the sink just behind you.
Put the pan down on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn to the other counters on the left.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn back to the pan.
Place the potato in the pan.
Turn back to the area you got the tomato from.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn back to the pan with the potato.
Slice the potato in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Slice a whole potato in a pan.

high_descs: Turn right at the door, go across to the fridge.
Grab the pan out of the fridge.
Turn around to the countertop beside the sink in the kitchen.
Place the pan on the countertop to the left of the sink.
Turn left to the avocado in the plate on the countertop.
Pick up the potato in the plate.
Turn around to the pan beside the sink.
Place the potato in the pan on the counter beside the sink.
Turn to the countertop closer to the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Go back to the potato.
Slice the potato in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a potato in a pan on the countertop in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn around and head out of this room, then head left into the kitchen, going to the fridge on the end at the left.
Remove the pan from the fridge.
Turn around to the countertop.
Place the pan on the countertop to the left of the sink.
Turn to the countertop on the left.
Pick up the potato.
Turn back to the pan.
Place the potato down on the pan.
Turn back to the countertop on the left.
Pick up the knife.
Turn back towards the potato.
Slice the potato in the pan.
anns.task_desc: Slice a Potato in a Pan on a CounterTop.
